  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for gpg2",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for gpg2 fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity fixes:\n\n- CVE-2026-24882: Fixed stack-based buffer overflow in TPM2 \n  PKDECRYPT for TPM-backed RSA and ECC keys (bsc#1257396)\n- Fixed GnuPG accepting Path Separators and Path Traversals in Literal \n  Data 'Filename' Field (bsc#1256389)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
